latestIgtvVideos.title: Sizzlers at home - a special rainy day request recipe !
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sauce - peri peri 🧡🧡
- Roast red capsicum in the oven , peel and grind and make a purée 
- chop garlic & celery and cook in a pan for 5 mins 
- Add purée , add some stock , some SNAPPIN peri Peri powder ( use this one for the perfect taste ) 
- add chilly flakes 
- if you need a thicker consistency add corn flour ( not directly mix one small spoon in hot water & add this mixture ) 

Step 1 
Prepare chicken in a basic marination herbs, garlic , olive oil , egg whites, lemon zest and lemon marinate for 1 hour and cook or grill. 

Step 2 
Cook vegetarian cutlets with paneer or potato and vegetables , bind it with bread or oats and shallow fry it/ bake it 

Step 3 
Cook all vegetables with herbs and garlic & olive oil 

Step 4 
Spinach in a white sauce or just melt cheese and garlic. I keep it healthy on other days and just toss it. 

Step 5 
Sweet potato or regular fries ( baked or fried ) 

Basically prepare anything you want 
Assemble and watch 

Use melted butter in water to give it that sizzling effect 

Ps - the assembly is the main thing 
The ingredients can totally depend upon your taste buds and likes. 

I did my best in showcasing how to do it yourself but if you have any questions, please send them in below 

Happy cooking 

#sizzlers #rainyday #foodforthought #recipes #TICrecipes #foodblogger #lockdowncooking #cookingathome #cookingvideos #cookwithT

CONQUERING my fears … one day at a time 
Back to work after baby #2 and honestly, I had so many questions running through my mind.

Truth is, I didn’t have a clear plan. I just knew I wanted to try. Because work doesn’t pause. And neither does motherhood.

Here’s to the version of us that’s still learning, still growing and still choosing to show up even when it’s messy, even when it’s hard 💛

So to all you moms out there trying to balance work and life, you’re not alone & we got this! 💪🏻

(parenting, motherhood, second time mom, work life balance, personal story, lifestyle , confession , ordinary , working mom )
